While 1st Secretary General of NATO, Lord Ismay is also credited as
having been the first person to say that the purpose of NATO was
"to keep the Soviet Union out, the Americans in, and the Germans
down," a saying that has since become a common way to describe the
dynamics of NATO.

Namen pridruzitve Rusije v NATO se je koncal z: "But things blew up
in the early 2000s as NATO’s eastern expansion plan, excluding
Russia, was moving in full force."

Dodal bi se vlogo reketa pri futranju orozarske industrije in to je
cirka to.
